Title: Flexzilla Pro Air Hose Reusable Fitting 1/4"
description:
This replacement hose end can make your Flexzilla and Flexzilla Pro air hose field repairable with three basic steps:

  1. Cut damaged portion of hose at 90 degrees. Slide bend restrictor and fitting nut onto hose.
  2. Push hose onto reusable fitting until hose reaches threads.
  3. Tighten fitting nut until snug. Snap into bend restrictor

Title: Colors SwivelGrip Garden Hose, 5/8" x 50'
description: From the makers of Flexzilla, Colors Garden Hose makes it easier to work around your home and lawn. SwivelGrip action eliminates twists that occur when uncoiling a hose. Conventional garden hose can trap coils that tighten into kinks as you move across the yard. SwivelGrip releases these trapped coils because the hose rotates freely inside the grip. The large, comfortable gripping surface on both ends of the hose makes connections much easier to turn and tighten. Colors Garden Hose features the same Flexible Hybrid Polymer material as our renowned ZillaGreen hoses, but comes in earthy colors that blend in with a variety of landscapes.

Title: Flexzilla Garden Hose, 5/8" x 25'
description: Flexzilla garden hose was engineered with a lightweight flexible hybrid polymer to lie ﬂat and eliminate kinking under pressure. It redeﬁnes ﬂexibility, making it easy to maneuver around trees, bushes or other obstacles. Zero memory means your sprinkler stays put without twisting. And flexzilla garden hose doesn’t ﬁght you when you coil it. Plus, with our superior O-ring, you get a long-term, leak-free connection at the spigot. The flexible hybrid polymer inner tube material is drinking water safe.

Title: ACT Cable Tie Removal Tool With Side Cutter

It redeﬁnes ﬂexibility, making it easy to maneuver around trees, bushes or other obstacles. Zero memory means your sprinkler stays put without twisting. And flexzilla garden hose doesn’t ﬁght you when you coil it. Plus, with our superior O-ring, you get a long-term, leak-free connection at the spigot. The flexible hybrid polymer inner tube material is drinking water safe.

Title: Flexzilla Pro Air Hose Reusable Fitting 3/8"
description:
Reusable fittings can be customized and repaired on job site. In just a few simple steps you can easily create a custom length hose assembly for your specific needs.

  1.  Cut damaged portion of hose at 90 degrees. Slide bend restrictor and fitting nut onto hose.
  2. Push hose onto reusable fitting until hose reaches threads.
  3. Tighten fitting nut until snug, then snap into bend restrictor.

Title: Flexzilla SwivelGrip Garden Hose, 5/8" x 50'
description: Flexzilla makes it easier to work around your home and lawn. SwivelGrip action eliminates twists that occur when uncoiling a hose. Conventional garden hose can trap coils that tighten into kinks as you move across the yard. SwivelGrip releases these trapped coils because the hose rotates freely inside the grip. The large, comfortable gripping surface on both ends of the hose makes connections much easier to turn and tighten. SwivelGrip hoses are also drinking water safe.
